                  </rs>. <hi rend="italic">When called upon to plead, he remained mute, and a Jury was sworn to try whether he was mute of malice or by the visitation of God, and upon the evidence of <persName id="t18670506-name-148" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18670506-name-148" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18670506-name-148" type="surname" value="GIBSON"></interp>
